Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天一直期待着和你一起的休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好的杏子姐的照片  快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  一定是三只大猫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直从你那里拿  真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  能拍几张轰的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的照片  拍了也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这种事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田  别杵在那里
